+    // ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
+    // FORMAL PROOF: Unsafe Set Completeness
+    //
+    // Theorem: Every state in the unsafe target set has V*(x) ≤ 0,
+    // and conversely, every state with V*(x) = UNSAFE_PENALTY is in
